{"tid":853650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1人1件同另一半既搞笑事","createTime":"2018-10-08T17:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T19:43:47.000Z","uid":211656,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c24ce1a2431c5841f94bb44fd1af68b6f43d5c","tid":853650,"uid":211656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:49:05.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有日同男朋友仔去食糖水<br />\n佢食朱古力心太軟食到成嘴都係<br />\n就叫佢抹乾淨<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  男朋友：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂 仲未抹乾淨呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（抹抹抹）得未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你咁抹點抹得乾淨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抹完一下仲用同一個位抹第二到（回抹）你咁同抹完屎咁 抹完再用屎抹有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我話都未講完 佢就一野咀左落嚟<br />\n仲講左句：食屎啦你<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58e9d87a0d06f17d616dd078cc8ed215e0f446a","tid":853650,"uid":211656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:04:13.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"dcef35cf7bb0016627bf894c0b62fc6f0879acb2","tid":853650,"uid":111751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"c0c493406c19db973ce4b9accc6f5193b7df4ea4","tid":853650,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T18:42:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">gay</span>"},{"pid":"60376f05cb99c88231a942cb12cc862a7badb124","tid":853650,"ui